import React from 'react' import { useEffect } from 'react' import { useDispatch, useSelector } from 'react-redux' import { getUlList } from '../../Actions/MainActions' import {Link} from 'react-router-dom' function UlList() { const ulList = useSelector(state => state.Data.ulList) const dispatch = useDispatch() useEffect(() => { dispatch(getUlList()) }, []) return (
    {ulList.product} {ulList.services} {ulList.about}
) } export default UlList
